snippet.title: Diana and Roma Learn about Bees, HATTA Honey Bee Garden Tour - Fun family trip
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma Learn about Bees, HATTA Honey Bee Garden Tour!
Diana and Roma learned about the different jobs that the bees have and the process that they use to make honey.  It was such a great experience to be able to hold a frame covered in bees.  After our tour of the Hatta #Honey #Bee Garden, we went inside to sample the honey. The honey was delicious!  The tour, honey, and whole experience was fantastic. 
Thanks for watching!
